                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17911026-2-victim66 t17911026-2-viclabel12"></join>, were married in this church by licence, the 15th day of September 1791; I have attested the marriage, the prisoner is the same man that was married, by that name, at our church.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17911026-2-person72">
                  THOMAS
                   CHARLES
               <interp inst="t17911026-2-person72" type="surname" value="CHARLES"></interp>
